parts.text:
Design a premium tented place card for an event. The card is 3.5 inches wide by 2 inches tall when folded. Show the FRONT face only, flat, from directly above.

Guest name: {guest_name}
Table: {table_name}
Event type: {event_category}
Style: {design_style}
Color palette: primary {color_primary}, accent {color_accent}
Background: {bg_color}

Design requirements:
- The guest name should be the focal point, centered, elegant and clearly readable
- Table assignment below the name in smaller text
- Include subtle decorative elements that match the {design_style} style
- Clean margins, professional print-ready quality
- No bleeding edges, white border around the design
- Photorealistic rendering as if it were a real printed card on a table
- Aspect ratio should be landscape (wider than tall)

Do NOT include any watermarks, logos, or placeholder text.

Create a seamless decorative background pattern for a premium event place card.

Style: {design_style}
Event type: {event_category}
Color palette: {color_primary}, {color_accent} on {bg_color}
Brand colors: {brand_colors}

Requirements:
- Subtle, elegant pattern that won't overwhelm text placed on top
- Very low contrast so text remains readable
- Seamless/tileable
- No text, no names, no words — pattern only
- Suitable for professional print at 300 DPI
- Style should evoke: {mood_keywords}

Output a flat rectangular image with no perspective or 3D effects.

You are a professional event designer. Create a cohesive name card design theme for the following event.

Event type: {event_category}
Venue type: {venue_type}
Brand colors: {brand_colors}
Season/time: {season}
Guest count: {guest_count}

Return a JSON object with exactly this structure:
{
  "name": "Theme name",
  "font_heading": "CSS font-family for the guest name",
  "font_body": "CSS font-family for table/details",
  "bg_color": "#hex background",
  "text_color": "#hex primary text",
  "accent_color": "#hex accent/decorative",
  "border_style": "none | thin | ornate | double",
  "border_color": "#hex",
  "decorative_elements": ["top-flourish", "corner-ornament", etc.],
  "texture": "none | linen | marble | watercolor | foil",
  "mood": "one-word mood descriptor"
}

Generate 4 distinct themes that would work well for this event. Return only valid JSON as an array of 4 objects.

Design a beautiful event program cover page.

Event name: {event_name}
Date: {event_date}
Location: {event_location}
Event type: {event_category}
Color palette: {color_primary}, {color_accent}
Brand colors: {brand_colors}

Requirements:
- Portrait orientation (5.5" x 8.5")
- Event name prominently displayed
- Date and location in smaller text
- Professional, print-ready design
- Elegant decorative elements matching the event style
- No placeholder images or stock photos
- Clean margins suitable for trimming

Render as a flat, top-down view of the printed cover.

Create a stylized, illustrated venue map for event guests.

Venue type: {venue_type}
Key areas to label: {areas}
Style: {design_style}
Color palette: {color_primary}, {color_accent}

Requirements:
- Bird's eye view, isometric or flat illustration style
- Clear labels for each area
- Warm, inviting illustration style (not a technical blueprint)
- Include icons for restrooms, exits, food areas if relevant
- Landscape orientation
- Print-ready quality

This should look like a hand-drawn or digitally illustrated wayfinding map, not a CAD drawing.
